<dl id="gn1002c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="gn1" href="#gn1002">GN1 </a>  <a href="../../ff/unbs/gn1all.htm#gn1002c"> (Dzierbicki) 2(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> A ricefield near Vercelli under creamy summer haze. The wings / of her drooping hat shadow her false smile. Shadows streak / her falsely smiling face, smitten by the hot creamy light, / grey wheyhued shadows under the jawbones, streaks of / eggyolk yellow on the moistened brow, rancid yellow / humour lurking within the softened pulp of the eyes.</blockquote> </dl>
